2010-08-05  Luis Fernando Muñoz Mejías <Luis.Fernando.Munoz.Mejias@cern.ch>

	* Release: 2.0.5
	- Condrestart instead of reload the service.

	At instalation time, if no post_reboot script was used, we saw the
	component failing because ssh hadn't started yet. This fixes the
	issue.

